OL,4,CCovid: Wales' NHS doctors 'bullied for
OL,5,Craising safety fears'
OL,6, Doctors in Wales have faced bullying
OL,7, and disciplinary action for raising
OL,8, concerns over working conditions and
OL,9, safety, a union leader has said.
OL,11,FDr Phil Banfield, of BMA Wales, said
OL,12,Fdoctors who complained about work, both
OL,13,Fbefore and during the Covid pandemic,
OL,14,Fwere seen as "troublemakers".
OL,16,FHe said there are worries bullying
OL,17,Famong staff will get worse as longer
OL,18,Fpost-Covid waiting lists are tackled.
OL,20,FThe Welsh government said bullying of
OL,21,FNHS staff was "entirely unacceptable".
